          "text": "Your terminal should return the exact text you wrote in your script, validating that your local setup is functioning correctly. You have successfully configured a system that keeps your project dependencies isolated and your core machine stable. The foundation of your workspace is complete. You can now move forward with building models and analyzing your own data.",
